data.description: 2020 UPDATES:  new kitchen remodel with new stainless appliances; Quartz countertops; utility bathroom remodel; other 2 bathrooms new tub/shower; new metal roof; paint and new vinyl plank floors throughout.2022 UPDATES:  new ECO view double pane windows throughout (with 1x transfer to new owner); new RUUD hvac inside and out (highest bill since hasn't gone over 200); 4-camera surveillance system with TV monitor; wired for alarm; 15'' blown-in attic insulation.  GAS:  fireplace, stove, AC furnace; water heater and gas hookup on patio for outdoor cooking. 10x16 shed with 2 lofts.  SELLER OFFERING HOME WARRANTY AT CLOSING FOR BUYER.
